R1 and R2 independently are

- C1-8 -alkyl, C2-8 alkenyl, C2-8 alkynyl, or C3-8 cycloalkyl, each optionally substituted with halogen, OH, NH2, NHR4, N(R4)2, NHCOR4, C1-4 alkoxy, trifluoromethoxy, carbamoyl, CONHR4, or CON(R4)2);


- H, Halogen, CF3, CF1-6 alkoxy, C1-6 alkylthio, OCF3, COOH, ON, CONH2, CONHR4, OH, NH2, NHR4, N(R4)2, NHCOR4, CON(R4)2, CONHSO2 R4, SO2 NH2, SO2 NHR4, C1-4 alkoxycarbonyl, phenyl, alkylphenyl, or tetrazole;


