- C1-8 -alkyl, C2-8 alkenyl, C2-8 alkynyl, or C3-6 cycloalkyl, each optionally substituted with halogen, OH, NH2, NHR4, N(R4)2, NHCOR4, C1-4 alkoxy, trifluoromethoxy, carbamoyl, CONHR4, or CON(R4)2 ;


